  "title": "Pirkei Avot §avot_02_13: Rabbi Shimon said: Be careful with the reading of Shema and the prayer, And w...",
  "body": "Rabbi Shimon said: Be careful with the reading of Shema and the prayer, And when you pray, do not make your prayer something automatic, but a plea for compassion before God, for it is said: “for He is gracious and compassionate, slow to anger, abounding in kindness, and renouncing punishment” (Joel 2:13); And be not wicked in your own esteem.",
